{"tid":1022239,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自來水管流出石油…伊拉克貧民窟居民大怒","createTime":"2019-02-15T01:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T05:59:30.000Z","uid":32511,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfb578a496f6fc1ef3a2f75071bc73dc5dac357","tid":1022239,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpkEcoj2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpkEcoj2.jpg&h=dfbb88e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊拉克缺水嚴重，已經爆發民眾抗議，而當地蘇瑪利亞電視台（Al Sumariya TV）更報導，卡爾巴拉省加季爾區約40多棟居民樓自來水管竟然流出石油，而不是飲用水，更致居民爆怒，要求當地立刻解決，否則將再舉行抗議示威。<br />\n <br />\n綜合媒體報導，加季爾區位於卡爾巴拉市郊，被認為是該市最大貧困區之一，早就陷在缺水的困境中，此次竟然從水管流出石油，更讓缺水問題惡化。<br />\n <br />\n據報導，伊拉克缺水嚴重，從去年7年開始，南部巴士拉市就爆發民眾抗議，接著漫延到各地，當局成立一個特別委員會，向居民承諾要撥款恢復飲用水及電網系統。"},{"pid":"5fa13c081f28adab7b998471ab8c118e08c45df2","tid":1022239,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:03:49.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"28914e78fb5db5270a804a6df9305a2e15b780b0","tid":1022239,"uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:05:28.000Z","msg":"俾你拎去賣到錢都冇用<br />\n根本冇水飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61b0e92bfcb819b22928f35ca299c5d78ec67a2","tid":1022239,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9ded6ed77879d0db9976b3031b8ae2bf49e6770","tid":1022239,"uid":32588,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"水貴過石油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4f41ba1c0a97cf86abe658ccbf46e68cd031d2","tid":1022239,"uid":5267,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T01:10:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b03ce2fab0acaf18e4b69eb8c2c4ae1fbe1c2e5","tid":1022239,"uid":228854,"like"